steps.html_instructions: Head east on W Allegan St toward Townsend St
Take the Interstate 496 W ramp on the left
Take the exit on the left onto I-69 S/I-96 E toward Ft Wayne/Detroit

Keep right at the fork to continue on I-69 S, follow signs for Ft Wayne
Entering Indiana
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-465 S/IN-37 and merge onto I-465 S/IN-37 S
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Jefferson Street and merge onto E Jefferson St

Turn right onto S 5th St
Destination will be on the right
